snippet.title: Developing Tori | Kyōryū Official Game Dev BTS
snippet.description:
Check out some behind the scenes clips of our Juvenile Tyrannosaurus Rex, Tori, in development for the Kyōryū First Playable! 

The latest game build for Kyōryū is making its exclusive debut at Gamescom 2024 with Floating Rock Studio CEO Lukas Niklaus attending this year.

Featuring an original track composed for the game by Jeffery Brice

❤️ Dimetrodon / Yama Tier Patrons saw this first!
